<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1910" box="[1117,1242,693,718]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Crocidura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="122" pageNumber="536" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="monax">C. monax</taxonomicName>
clade and seems to be sister to C. munissii; together they are close to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1904" box="[1100,1233,764,797]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Crocidura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="122" pageNumber="519" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fumosa">C. fumosa</taxonomicName>
. 
