<subSubSection pageId="122" pageNumber="519" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="122.[122,1328,884,1666]" pageId="122" pageNumber="519">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[124,481,1514,1547]" pageId="122" pageNumber="519">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. Mduma’s White-toothed Shrew is threatened largely from small farms that might result in habitat loss in its small distribution. It occurs in the Ngorongoro Conservation Area.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
